title: BRIEF-Kirkland Lake Gold Says 147,644 Ounces Produced In Q1 2018, An Increase Of 13 Pct
text:
April 6, 2018 / 11:50 AM / in 10 minutes BRIEF-Kirkland Lake Gold Says 147,644 Ounces Produced In Q1 2018, An Increase Of 13 Pct Reuters Staff 
April 6 (Reuters) - Kirkland Lake Gold Ltd: 
* KIRKLAND LAKE GOLD REPORTS STRONG YEAR-OVER-YEAR Q1 PRODUCTION GROWTH 
* KIRKLAND LAKE GOLD LTD - REMAINS ON TRACK TO ACHIEVE ITS FULL-YEAR 2018 PRODUCTION GUIDANCE OF OVER 620,000 OUNCES 
* KIRKLAND LAKE GOLD - 147,644 OUNCES WAS PRODUCED IN Q1 2018, AN INCREASE OF 13% Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
